tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Study_Participants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  study_group VARCHAR(20),
  enrollment_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE telepsychiatry_study (
  study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  study_name VARCHAR(255),
  study_description TEXT,
  study_start_date DATE,
  study_end_date DATE,
  researcher_name VARCHAR(100),
  location VARCHAR(100),
  participants_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE telepsychiatry_interventions (
  intervention_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  intervention_name VARCHAR(255),
  intervention_description TEXT,
  intervention_type VARCHAR(50),
  study_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (study_id) REFERENCES telepsychiatry_study(study_id)
);

CREATE TABLE telepsychiatry_interventions (study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
patient_id INT,
intervention_type VARCHAR(50),
intervention_date DATE,
outcome VARCHAR(50));

CREATE TABLE patients (patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
patient_name VARCHAR(100),
age INT,
gender VARCHAR(10),
contact_number VARCHAR(15));

CREATE TABLE research_studies (study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
study_name VARCHAR(100),
researcher_name VARCHAR(100),
start_date DATE,
end_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE research_studies (
 study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 study_title TEXT,
 study_description TEXT,
 start_date DATE,
 end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE participants (
 participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 study_id INT,
 participant_name TEXT,
 gender TEXT,
 age INT,
 FOREIGN KEY (study_id) REFERENCES research_studies(study_id)
)

CREATE TABLE interventions (
 intervention_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 intervention_name TEXT,
 intervention_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE study_results (
 result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 study_id INT,
 participant_id INT,
 intervention_id INT,
 result_description TEXT,
 result_date DATE,
 FOREIGN KEY (study_id) REFERENCES research_studies(study_id),
 FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES participants(participant_id),
 FOREIGN KEY (intervention_id) REFERENCES interventions(intervention_id)
)

CREATE TABLE ResearchStudies (
  study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  study_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  researcher_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE Participants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name VARCHAR(255),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  study_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (study_id) REFERENCES ResearchStudies(study_id)
);

CREATE TABLE TherapySessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_date DATE,
  session_duration TIME,
  participant_id INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (session_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES Participants(participant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE SessionFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (feedback_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES TherapySessions(session_id)
);
